      • getContactrefOrPolygonOrWireOrVia

        public java.util.List<java.lang.Object> getContactrefOrPolygonOrWireOrVia()
        Gets the value of the contactrefOrPolygonOrWireOrVia property.

        This accessor method returns a reference to the live list, not a snapshot. Therefore any modification you make to the returned list will be present inside the JAXB object. This is why there is not a set method for the contactrefOrPolygonOrWireOrVia property.

        For example, to add a new item, do as follows: 

         getContactrefOrPolygonOrWireOrVia().add(newItem);
